{"id":1582,"date":"2018-06-01T09:50:31","date_gmt":"2018-06-01T09:50:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=1582"},"modified":"2021-02-27T08:42:27","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T08:42:27","slug":"nhung-sai-lam-chet-nguoi-thuong-gap-trong-thiet-ke-noi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/nhung-sai-lam-chet-nguoi-thuong-gap-trong-thiet-ke-noi\/","title":{"rendered":"Sai l\u1ea7m ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00f4ng k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m, thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang ta t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi v\u00ec ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i b\u1ea1n ch\u1ee3t nh\u1eadn ra nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ednh th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, kh\u00f4ng h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sai l\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t:<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed7i c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng mang m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau t\u1eeb m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1583\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u1ebb con lu\u00f4n thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0 duy, s\u1edf th\u00edch theo theo gian, do \u0111\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf l\u00fac c\u00f2n b\u00e9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u00e9 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi l\u1edbn l\u00ean. V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a khi ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o l\u1ea1i c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1585\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pngu1c-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pngu1c-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pngu1c-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pngu1c-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pngu1c.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham lam nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft, tranh trang tr\u00ed<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham lam nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, tranh,\u2026., nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y nh\u1edb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u m\u1eabu c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ebb h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1586\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/4.jpg 564w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/4-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/4-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/4-250x250.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1587\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/7-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/7-1.jpg 563w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/7-1-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00e8n noen<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00e8n noen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam h\u01a1n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1ea5m c\u00fang, h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t d\u00e2y \u0111\u00e8n trang tr\u00ed v\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1588\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"579\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5.jpg 563w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 579px) 100vw, 579px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Bi\u1ebfn ban c\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh n\u01a1i l\u01b0u tr\u1eef \u0111\u1ed3<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ban c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i l\u01b0u tr\u1eef \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u0103n h\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 m\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1eeba b\u1ed9n. H\u00e3y t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i \u1ea5m c\u00fang cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian b\u00ean nhau th\u00ec sao?<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1589\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\